video_title: Signs Someone Is Lying To Themselves
transcript:
I'm a psychologist and here's three
signs someone is lying to themselves
without knowing it number one they avoid
friends and family that they know will
be honest with them about their actions
they can only be around people who
reinforce their behavior number two as
soon as someone questions their choices
they become defensive aggressive or even
shut down completely and avoid them and
number three they play Down ignore or
completely deny the damage they're
causing around them
